content.rendered:
Directed by Vishal Mishra.

Written by Aabhar Dadhich. Aabhar Dadhich. Vishal Mishra.

Cast Sunil Grover(Arnab). Zakir Hussain(D). Yugant Badri Pandey(Terrorist (as Yugant Pandey)). Vinod pal Singh Raghuwanshi(Kidanaper). Ajay Raj(Kidnapper). Dipannita Sharma(Neha). Rajesh Sharma(Channel owner). Anjana Sukhani(Parul). Pankaj Tripathi(Girdhari)

Language Hindi

Producers Ankit Chandiramani. Amit Choudhary. Dhanashree Mehta. Vinod Ramani. Mohan Sachdev. Manan Sampat. Salman m Shaikh.

Production Apex Entertainment.
